snippet.title: Grand Theft Auto: Vice City - Anniversary Trailer
snippet.description:
To commemorate the anniversary of Vice City and its mobile release on select Android devices, please enjoy this nostalgia-filled Anniversary Video celebrating a decade since the original game's launch. Grand Theft Auto: Vice City 10th Anniversary Edition is now available for select Android devices from Google Play.

www.rockstargames.com/vicecity/anniversary

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood and Gore, Violence, Strong Language, Strong Sexual Content, Violence
